        <p>same as color name "tomato", but 50% transparent:</p>

        <h1 style="background-color: rbga(255, 99, 71, 0.5);">grb(255, 99, 71, 0.5)</h1>
        <h1 style="background-color: hsla(9, 100%, 64%, 0.5);">hsla(9, 100%, 64%, 0.5)</h1>
        <p>in addition to the perdefined color names, color can be specifiend using RBG, HEX, HSL, or even transparent colors using RGBA or HSLA color values</p>
